race.comment: LEGACY BEL (12) will prove the testing material, having found only one better at her past two starts and having the benefit of gate 2 here. She should be prominent throughout. ILOVEDIAMONDS (11) hasn't placed in three starts this time in, but she's been on the placegetters' heels and they have been in tougher races than this. BIG ROOSTER (1) is another first-starter who has impressed at the jumpouts. EPOCH (2) should be better for the debut prep, when he only had one start for a fourth placing, and recent jumpouts suggest he has come on. Has placed at 3 of 5 starts and turned in an encouraging recent Ballarat jumpout performance in preparation for this.
